headline: 2 Reasons to Like URI and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Over the last six months, United Rentals shares have sunk to $708.20, producing a disappointing 17.4% loss - worse than the S&P 500’s 2.4% drop. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
